<h2 id="bible" class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2 mt-4">Narrative Bible</h2>
<p>Our goal for the Narrative Bible was to provide an easily accessible and navigable guide to all things narrative and world building. You can read more about our narrative process and decisions.</p>
