{# LESSON 3 #}
<div class="mb-8 rounded-lg p-2 mt-8 border border-purple-200 dark:border-purple-800 bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/20 rounded-lg">
  <h3 id="learned4" class="font-semibold">Lesson 4: Write LESS</h3>
    <p class="ml-8">Through playtesting, players became disengaged with narrative if conversations dragged on for too long. Much of our revision included getting key info to the player with as few words as possible. With more time, we would have made the writing even more concise.</p>
</div>


